    "I know there are places, there are meetings for people with chronic pain to chat, have a coffee, and things like that.",
    "We don't have that here.",
    "I found it fun to listen to them and know we're not alone in this.",
    "[ INT 9] On the one hand, interviewees thought the weekly connection and review of personal objectives supported their motivation and helped them stay focused: I guess I needed to be held by the hand for a while, and to be guided through it...",
    "There was some kind of follow-up."
